<a href="/questions/831455-having-read-john-kabat-zinn-s-full">Having read John Kabat-Zinn&#39;s &quot;Full Castastrophe Living,&quot; and having taken the 8-week mindfulness meditation class locally (based on his teachings), will there be new material for me in this book? Many thanks.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_831455'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11350120-mindfulness">like</a></span>

