        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3210555786" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1362521429414737626">A book that met what it claimed and what I required. <br/><br/>What impressed me was that the book covered psychological (how our mind responds to stress), biological (how our body responds to stress) and Execution plan (8 week simple exercise to inculcate mindful thinking in our routine). It addressed all dimensions comprehensively.<br/><br/>I researched a lot about books that talked about Mindfulness. But this happened to be a perfect destination to my search. <br/><br/>Definitely a good read for anyone looking for a solut</span>
  <span id="freeText1362521429414737626" style="display:none">A book that met what it claimed and what I required. <br /><br />What impressed me was that the book covered psychological (how our mind responds to stress), biological (how our body responds to stress) and Execution plan (8 week simple exercise to inculcate mindful thinking in our routine). It addressed all dimensions comprehensively.<br /><br />I researched a lot about books that talked about Mindfulness. But this happened to be a perfect destination to my search. <br /><br />Definitely a good read for anyone looking for a solution to the stress created by corporate life (which is actually created by us internally)<br /><br />Perspective - <br />We can't control our thoughts, but we can control how we relate to those thoughts!<br /><br /><br />Regards <br />Saravana</span>
  <a data-text-id="1362521429414737626" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


